                                                worden sein, bekümert hab und im der niht volgen
                                                wöll lassen. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> sun durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weisen wöllet,
                                                daz er <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> an
